<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="./styles.css" rel="stylesheet" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.4.1/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-wfSDF2E50Y2D1uUdj0O3uMBJnjuUD4Ih7YwaYd1iqfktj0Uod8GCExl3Og8ifwB6" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>About JS_Quiz_Maker</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

<%- include('../views/partials/header'); %>

<div class="container mt-4">

    <!-- Title -->
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4">JavaScript Quiz Maker</h1>
            <h2 class="lead">A dynamic and cross-platform quiz creation tool for all JavaScript enthusiasts!</h2>
            <p class="lead" style="font-size: 15px;">OFFICIAL VERSION <%= version %></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Description and Features -->
    <div class="row justify-content-center mt-2 ">
        <div class="col-md-8 ">
            <h2>About JS_Quiz_Maker</h2>
            <p>JS_Quiz_Maker is crafted for educators, developers, and all those passionate about JavaScript. This Electron-based desktop application merges the power of Node.js and Express, offering an intuitive platform for quiz creation and management.</p>
            <p>Why limit your knowledge to conventional learning methods? Dive deep into JavaScript, challenge your skills, or simply engage your students in an interactive learning environment.</p>
            
            <h3 class="mt-4">Features</h3>
            <ul class = "list-unstyled font-weight-bold">
                <li>- Design captivating quizzes using a simple text file, and bring them to life in our tailor-made GUI.</li>
                <li>- Instant quiz scoring and actionable feedback - a step towards perfection.</li>
                <li>- Share the joy of learning: Distribute your quizzes easily with text file sharing.</li>
                <li>- A seamless editor interface to craft and modify JavaScript quizzes.</li>
                <li>- Multiple-choice questions? You got it. Customize options as per your needs.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</div>

<p>________</p>

<%- include('../views/partials/footer'); %>

</body>
